{"title": "Thrill Book Vol. II No. 3, August 1, 1919", "description": "Welcome to another edition of the exciting and influential pulp magazine The Thrill Book!  In this issue, we bring you \"The Unknown Revolution\", a sensational novel of revolutionary action and intrigue in Mexico!  We also conclude the dashing lost city adventure \"The Lost Empire\" and begin the strange and mysterious 2-parter \"The Lost Days\" as well as continuing the seafaring pirate tale \"The Opium Ship\"!  For those who like their stories steeped in the macabre, we have returning author Greye La Spina with the spine-tingling \"The Wax Doll\", the psychical happenings of \"The Crystal Ball\", the bizarre invention of \"When Dead Lips Speak\" and the psychologically sinister \"The Spider and the Fly\".  Plus another installment of the mind-bending world of The Double Man!  All this and more await thrill-seekers and voracious readers alike! - Summary by Ben Tucker", "duration": 33121, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "18", "name": " Various"}], "coverArt": "https://archive.org/download/thrillbookvol2no3_2603_librivox/thrill2_3_2603.jpg", "copyright_year": "1919", "genres": ["Action & Adventure Fiction", "Horror & Supernatural Fiction", "Periodicals & Magazines"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "LibriVox Volunteers"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "Ben Tucker"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "Annise"}, {"role": "Proof Listener", "name": "Cbteddy"}], "sections": [{"section": 1, "title": "The Unknown Revolution by Denby Brixton Chapter I - VII", "readers": [12933], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/thrillbookvol2no3_2603_librivox/thrillbookvol2no3_01_various_64kb.mp3", "duration": 2421}, {"section": 2, "title": "The Unknown Revolution Chapter VIII-XI", "readers": [12933], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/thrillbookvol2no3_2603_librivox/thrillbookvol2no3_02_various_64kb.mp3", "duration": 2170}, {"section": 3, "title": "The Unknown Revolution Ch